Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_normali...ip_linear_part(25.10)  timing_normali...ip_linear_part(25.10)

Name
       timing_normalized_driver_waveform_clip_linear_part

Syntax
       timing_normalized_driver_waveform_clip_linear_part

       {0 | 1}

       Default: 0

       When set to 1, the linear ramp component in the normalized driver wave-
       form is saturated to the maximum value, while generating the normalized
       driver waveform.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

